Abstract: Direkt Proﬁl is an automatic analyzer of texts written in French as a second
language. The objective is to produce an evaluation of the development stage of the students
under the form of a learner profile. Direkt Proﬁl carries out a sentence analysis based on
developmental sequences, i.e. local morphosyntactic phenomena linked to a development in
the learning of French. The paper presents the corpus that we use and brieﬂy, the
developmental sequences. Furthermore, it describes the annotation that we have defined, the
parser, and the user interface. We conclude by the results obtained so far: on the test corpus
the systems obtains a recall of 83% and a precision of 83%.

